name: What is That ?
description:
MONOKROMONKEY
Digital Drawing
4133 x 4133 px
2021

The insights, stil coming from my childhoods moments (details on "That Power Ranger" artwork). That childhoods happen about couple decades far before now, but the impacts, remain until now. The fact that i got forbid to go out, hang around with other kids, screw my social life. I have to try hard to do that. I knooww, its a basic things, easy peasy, what a lame, bla bla bla bla bla, but here's the things, i try to adapt. its uncommon things for me, i used to socialize with pencils and papers. with a people, a "real people", thats a different things.

Pen and paper is a stuff, i understand the purpose they made. But a people ? What is that ? 

I think, people is complicated, sometimes i think i understand, but it means that i didn't. Sometimes honest tought as a good things, but it doesn't work when you apply that on several people, conditions, terms, feelings, ethics, places, and kind of asdjlasjklsd,aslkdjaksjdka,la;foejra,jawojfaksl;dk,ale;kfaskj,akljfaksdnoefalknaf,aekfjaknsdkad,alkjskasd asdhjkahsdu, asljdkaskd, screw it !
